# Zeno SVG Illustrations (Colors & Animation)

> Reference for styling and animating SVG illustrations to match the Zeno design system.

## Overview

All SVG illustrations should use colors from this palette to maintain visual consistency. When receiving new SVGs (from designers, stock sources, or AI generation), remap their colors to these values.

