## Color Replacements Applied

When modifying SVGs for Zeno, apply these transformations:

### Remove
```
#D8BF9B (large background rectangles) → DELETE the path entirely
```

### Replace Black Elements
```
#000000 → #4A2219 (Clay._800)
#0A0F0D → #4A2219 (Clay._800)
#1A1A1A → #4A2219 (Clay._800)
```

### Replace Cool Greys/Blues
```
#5D8691 (Silt/Teal) → #965846 (Clay._500) for organic elements
#8A918D (Moss Grey) → #D18C82 (Clay._400) for soft elements like clouds
```

### Keep As-Is
```
#CCFF00 (Acid Green) — Keep for energy/highlight elements
#B4913E (Brass Gold) — Keep for body/golden elements  
#D8BF9B (Sand) — Keep for skin tones (not backgrounds)
```

